                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>General aspects of the war in Europe, including planning for Operation <gloss
                        target="#t_Overlord1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Overlord</hi>
                    </gloss>, are included in this section. Papers, however, which deal exclusively
                    with Italian questions (peace feelers, surrender terms, and the status of Rome
                    as an open city) and with the question of bases in the Azores and in Ireland are
                    printed in separate sections below.</p>
            </div>
